it/tag/stefan-anton-reck/" rel="tag">Stefan Anton Reck</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/teatro-massimo-di-palermo/" rel="tag">Teatro Massimo di Palermo</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/thomas-gazheli/" rel="tag">Thomas Gazheli</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Christian Voigt, Deborah Leonetti, Graham Vick, Judit Kutasi, Megan Miller, Michael Eder, Opera lirica, Peter Bronder, recensioni, Richard Wagner, Sergei Leiferkus, Siegfried, Stefan Anton Reck, Teatro Massimo di Palermo, Thomas Gazheli"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/f56370b7da5e03bbc648642da149afc1" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2008/04/100_1873-140x200.jpg" width="70" height="100" alt="Ilaria Grippaudo" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Ilaria Grippaudo"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/ilaria-grippaudo/">View all articles by Ilaria Grippaudo</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2015/12/torino-teatro-regio-carmina-burana/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Torino, Teatro Regio: &#8220;Carmina Burana&#8221;</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2015/12/pisa-teatro-verdi-catone/" rel="next">Pisa, Teatro Verdi: &#8220;Catone&#8221; 